bigNumber

Class BigNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • bigNumber.BigNumber

  • public class BigNumber
extends java.lang.Object
    BigNumber provides basic arithmetic operations for large signed integers outside of the maximum values for primitive ints. BigNumber also provides a function that will find the two prime factors of a large number
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Tyler Robinson & Alex Tejada
